      <h3>Our Core Programmes</h3>

      <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
          <h4>Nutrition & Meal Support</h4>
          <p>
            We provide wholesome meals and nutritional assistance to children
            and families in need, helping improve health, school attendance,
            and overall well-being.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h4>Early Childhood & Community Care</h4>
          <p>
            Our outreach supports young children, mothers, and caregivers
            through food access, awareness sessions, and essential services
            that strengthen community health from the earliest stages of life.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h4>Education & Digital Learning</h4>
          <p>
            Saarthi promotes learning opportunities through scholarships,
            remedial education, and digital access programmes that empower
            students to continue their education with confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h4>School & Environment Development</h4>
          <p>
            We support safe and inspiring learning environments by improving
            school infrastructure, learning resources, and community
            participation in education.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h4>Emergency & Humanitarian Relief</h4>
          <p>
            During crises and natural disasters, Saarthi delivers food,
            essentials, and rapid assistance to affected communities,
            ensuring timely and compassionate support.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h4>Community Empowerment</h4>
          <p>
            Through awareness drives, volunteer engagement, and partnerships,
            we work to build stronger, self-reliant communities capable of
            sustaining long-term positive change.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
